name: FontDownloading
shortdesc: Options for downloading fonts to the printer.

property.name: NONE
property.shortdesc: Downloads only references to fonts. Note: Use when fonts reside in the printer.

property.name: COMPLETE
property.shortdesc: Downloads all fonts once per page.

property.name: SUBSET
property.shortdesc: Downloads only the characters &#40;glyphs) used in the document. Glyphs are downloaded once per page.

property.name: SUBSET_LARGE
property.shortdesc: Downloads only the characters &#40;glyphs) used in the document. Glyphs are downloaded once per page. Note: Use when the number of glyphs exceeds 350.
